20must%20accept%20the%20return%20of%20its%20citizens%20in%20a%20timely%20manner%20when%20another%20country...%20seeks%20to%20remove%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWashington%20%26quot%3Bwill%20be%20prepared%20to%20review%20these%20actions%20when%20South%20Sudan%20is%20in%20full%20cooperation%2C%26quot%3B%20Rubio%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20world's%20newest%20country%20and%20also%20one%20of%20the%20poorest%2C%20South%20Sudan%20is%20currently%20prey%20to%20tensions%20between%20political%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20observers%20fear%20a%20renewal%20of%20the%20civil%20war%20that%20killed%20400%2C000%20people%20between%202013%20and%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Sudanese%20nationals%20had%20been%20granted%20%26quot%3Btemporary%20protected%20status%26quot%3B%20(TPS)%20by%20the%20administration%20of%20Trump's%20predecessor%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20with%20the%20designation%20set%20to%20expire%20on%20May%203%2C%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20grants%20TPS%2C%20which%20shields%20people%20against%20deportation%2C%20to%20foreign%20citizens%20who%20cannot%20safely%20return%20home%20because%20of%20war%2C%20natural%20disasters%20or%20other%20%26quot%3Bextraordinary%26quot%3B%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20about%20133%20South%20Sudanese%20in%20the%20United%20States%20under%20the%20TPS%20program%2C%20with%20another%20140%20eligible%20to%20apply%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20said%20in%20September%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Trump%20White%20House%20has%20begun%20overturning%20TPS%20designations%2C%20revoking%20protection%20in%20January%20from%20more%20than%20600%2C000%20Venezuelans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20federal%20judge%20this%20week%20put%20that%20decision%20on%20hold%20after%20calling%20into%20question%20the%20government's%20claims%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20Venezuelans%20in%20the%20US%20were%20criminals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Pew%20Research%20Center%2C%20as%20of%2