s%20effortless%20ability%20to%20match%20Dosanjh's%20steps%20and%20embrace%20the%20vibrant%20Punjabi%20dance%20culture.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fwill-smith-nails-the-bhangra-diljit-dosanjh-declares-panjabi-aa-gaye-oye%2Farticleshow%2F120031241.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22All%20About%20New%20Pamban%20Bridge%2C%20India's%20First%20Vertical-Lift%20Sea%20Bridge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOver%20a%20century%20after%20the%20original%20Pamban%20Bridge%20was%20built%20across%20the%20Palk%20Strait%20in%20Rameswaram%2C%20India%20is%20set%20to%20launch%20a%20state-of-the-art%20replacement.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20will%20inaugurate%20the%20New%20Pamban%20Bridge%20-%20the%20country's%20first%20vertical-lift%20sea%20bridge%20-%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20on%20Sunday.%20Located%20in%20the%20Ramanathapuram%20district%2C%20the%20bridge%20connects%20Rameswaram%20Island%20with%20Mandapam%20on%20the%20mainland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIndia's%20Engineering%20Marvel%20is%20Here!%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20New%20Pamban%20Rail%20Bridge%20is%20India's%20first%20vertical%20lift%20sea%20bridge!%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%F0%9F%8C%89%20Rises%2017m%20high%20in%20just%205%20minutes%20for%20seamless%20maritime%20navigation%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%F0%9F%9A%86%20Strengthens%20connectivity%20between%20Rameswaram%20and%20mainland%20India%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%9C%A8%20Enables%20faster%2C%20smoother%20rail%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FwU2IeSMlb5%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FwU2IeSMlb5%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20MyGovIndia%20(%40mygovindia)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmygovindia%2Fstatus%2F1908530089735971163%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%205%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAll%20About%20The%20New%20Pamban%20Bridge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20New%20Pamban%20Bridge%20is%202.07%20kilometres%20long%20and%20spans%20across%20the%20Palk%20Strait%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20features%20a%2072.5-metre%20navigational%20span%20that%20can%20be%20vertically%20lifted%20to%2017%20metres%2C%20allowing%20ships%20to%20pass%20below%20safely.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20substructure%20can%20support%20two%20railway%20tracks%2C%20though%20it%20currently%20operates%20a%20single%20line.%20It%20connects%20Pamban%20(Rameswaram)%20Island%20with%20Mandapam%20on%20the%20mainland.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20bridge%20is%20cleared%20for%20train%20speeds%20up%20to%2080%20kmph%20and%20is%20built%20to%20handle%20increased%20rail%20traffic%20and%20heavier%20loads.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EConstructed%20by%20Rail%20Vikas%20Nigam%20Limited%20(RVNL)%2C%20a%20Navratna%20PSU%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Railways%2C%20the%20bridge%20cost%20approximately%20Rs%20550%20crore.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWith%20a%20projected%20lifespan%20of%20100%20years%2C%20the%20bridge%20has%20been%20constructed%20with%20special%20engineering%20techniques%20that%20reduce%20the%20need%20for%20frequent%20maintenance.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20uses%20stainless%20steel%20reinforcement%2C%20fully%20welded%20joints%2C%20high-grade%20protective%20paint%2C%20and%20a%20polysiloxane%20coating%20to%20protect%20against%20corrosion%20in%20the%20harsh%20marine%20environment.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20new%20bridge%20is%20built%203%20metres%20higher%20than%20the%20old%20one%2C%20offering%20better%20sea%20clearance%20for%20maritime%20traffic.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20lift%20span%20girder%20was%20assembled%20using%20the%20%26quot%3BAuto%20Launching%20Method%20based%20on%20Relationship%20Principle%2C%26quot%3B%20developed%20by%20Suntech%20Construction%20and%20verified%20by%20IIT%20Madras.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWorkers%20painted%20and%20inspected%20the%20girder%20segments%20offsite%2C%20transported%20them%20by%20truck%20to%20Pamban%2C%20and%20assembled%20them%20using%20EOT%20cranes%20on%20a%20temporary%20platform.%20Engineers%20used%20PAUT%20(Phased%20Array%20Ultrasonic%20Testing)%20to%20carry%20out%20precise%20welding%20checks.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20bridge%20is%20being%20compared%20to%20famous%20ones%20like%20the%20Golden%20Gate%20Bridge%20in%20the%20USA%2C%20Tower%20Bridge%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20and%20the%20Oresund%20Bridge%20between%20Denmark%20and%20Sweden%20because%20of%20its%20modern%20design%20and%20technology.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20original%20Pamban%20Bridge%2C%20built%20in%201914%20by%20British%20engineers%2C%20used%20a%20manually%20operated%20Scherzer's%20span%20(a%20type%20of%20rolling%20lift%20bridge).%20It%20had%20a%2061-metre%20truss%20that%20lifted%20up%20to%2081%20degrees%20for%20ship%20movement.%20That%20bridge%20has%20been%20shut%20to%20rail%20traffic%20due%20to%20safety%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743913920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2F4t1b7g3_new-pamban-bridge_625x300_06_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fall-about-new-pamban-bridge-indias-first-vertical-lift-sea-bridge-8098401%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Over%20a%20century%20after%20the%20original%20Pamban%20Bridge%20was%20built%20across%20the%20Palk%20Strait%20in%20Rameswaram%2C%20India%20is%20set%20to%20launch%20a%20state-of-the-art%20replacement.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jaaved%20Jaaferi%3A%20I%20may%20have%20made%20some%20wrong%20career%20decisions..%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743913800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-120015268%2Cimgsize-20030.cm