other%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20great%20if%20you%20guys%20stopped%20with%20the%20dehumanising%20posts!%20It's%20disgusting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20isn't%20policy.%20This%20is%20state-sponsored%20dehumanisation%20-%20with%20a%20soundtrack.%20Weaponising%20suffering.%20Mocking%20lives%20torn%20apart.%20Celebrating%20cruelty%20like%20it's%20a%20game%20show.%20This%20is%20how%20fascism%20talks%20when%20it%20thinks%20no%20one%20can%20stop%20it.%20We%20see%20you.%20And%20we%20will%20stop%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20another.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20official%20statement%20from%20the%20White%20House%2C%20in%20March%2C%20the%20US%20Border%20Patrol%20encountered%20just%207%2C181%20illegal%20immigrants%20at%20the%20southern%20border%20compared%20to%20the%20same%20month%20under%20former%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20-%20a%2095%20per%20cent%20decrease%20from%202024%20(137%2C473)%2C%20a%2096%20per%20cent%20decrease%20from%202023%20(163%2C672)%2C%20and%20a%2097%20per%20cent%20decrease%20from%202022%20(211%2C181).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20White%20House%20has%20released%20a%20video%20with%20pop%20songs%20playing%20in%20the%20background.%20Last%20month%2C%20a%20similar%20deportation%20video%20featuring%20the%20band%20Semisonic's%20'Closing%20Time'%20sparked%20controversy.%20The%20band%2C%20which%20was%20nominated%20for%20a%20Grammy%20for%20the%201998%20song%2C%20said%20the%20White%20House%20had%20used%20the%20song%20without%20permission%20and%20had%20entirely%20misunderstood%20its%20meaning.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743913140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fajne972_white-house-video-_625x300_06_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fna-na-na-na-na-na-na-na-white-houses-deportation-video-sparks-row-8098493%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20White%20House%20video%20showcasing%20the%20deportation%20of%20imm