arriage.%20So%20did%20Nikhil%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Najafgarh.%20According%20to%20Priyanka's%20brother%20Mohit%2C%20the%20couple%20remained%20close%20and%20supportive%20of%20each%20other's%20aspirations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20the%20couple%20reached%20the%20amusement%20park%20around%201%20pm%20on%20Thursday.%20After%20spending%20the%20early%20part%20of%20the%20day%20on%20water%20rides%2C%20they%20headed%20to%20the%20amusement%20section%20in%20the%20evening.%20At%20approximately%206%3A15%20pm%2C%20they%20boarded%20the%20roller%20coaster%20ride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENikhil%20told%20police%20that%20as%20the%20swing%20reached%20its%20highest%20point%2C%20a%20supporting%20stand%20broke%2C%20causing%20Priyanka%20to%20fall.%20Her%20injuries%20were%20severe.%20Police%20confirmed%20visible%20trauma%20on%20the%20body%2C%20including%20a%20laceration%20on%20the%20right%20leg%2C%20a%20puncture%20wound%20on%20the%20left%20leg%2C%20and%20other%20injuries%20on%20her%20forearm%20and%20knee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20arrived%20at%20the%20hospital%20to%20collect%20the%20medical%20report%20and%20later%20handed%20over%20the%20body%20to%20her%20family%20after%20a%20post-mortem.%20An%20FIR%20has%20been%20registered%20under%20sections%20289%20(negligent%20conduct%20with%20respect%20to%20animals%20or%20machinery)%20and%20106%20(culpable%20homicide%20not%20amounting%20to%20murder%20by%20negligence)%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20(BNS)%2C%20which%20recently%20replaced%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20no%20official%20comment%20yet%20from%20the%20management%20of%20Fun%20and%20Food%20Village.%20The%20park%20has%20not%20issued%20a%20statement%20or%20responded%20to%20media%20inquiries.%20The%20section%20of%20the%20park%20where%20the%20accident%20occurred%20remains%20shut.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743910440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fm8r2s4eg_delhi-woman-dies-_625x300_0