%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpponents%20of%20the%20Republican%20president's%20policies%20--%20from%20government%20staffing%20cuts%20to%20trade%20tariffs%20and%20eroding%20civil%20liberties%20--%20rallied%20in%20Washington%2C%20New%20York%2C%20Houston%2C%20Florida%2C%20Colorado%20and%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20among%20other%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20so%20angry%2C%20I'm%20so%20mad%2C%20all%20the%20time%2C%20yes.%20A%20bunch%20of%20privileged%2C%20white%20alleged%20rapists%20are%20controlling%20our%20country.%20It's%20not%20great%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20New%20York%20painter%20Shaina%20Kesner%2C%2043%2C%20joining%20a%20crowd%20marching%20through%20the%20heart%20of%20Manhattan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Washington%2C%20thousands%20of%20demonstrators%20--%20many%20traveling%20from%20across%20the%20United%20States%20--%20gathered%20on%20the%20National%20Mall%20where%20dozens%20of%20speakers%20rallied%20opposition%20to%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20about%20100%20people%20who%20have%20come%20down%20by%20bus%20and%20van%20from%20New%20Hampshire%20to%20protest%20against%20this%20outrageous%20administration%20(that)%20is%20causing%20us%20to%20lose%20our%20allies%20across%20the%20world%2C%20and%20causing%20devastation%20to%20people%20here%20at%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Diane%20Kolifrath%2C%2064%2C%20a%20bike%20tour%20guide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20gutting%20our%20government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20a%20woman%20dressed%20as%20a%20character%20from%20dystopian%20novel%20%26quot%3BThe%20Handmaid's%20Tale%26quot%3B%20waved%20a%20large%20flag%20with%20the%20message%3A%20%26quot%3BGet%20out%20of%20my%20uterus%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20reference%20to%20Trump's%20anti-abortion%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Denver%2C%20Colorado%2C%20one%20man%20in%20a%20large%20crowd%20of%20protesters%20held%20up%20a%20placard%20reading%20%26quot%3BNo%20king%20for%20USA.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe