nyway-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20felt%20embarrassed%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20not%20necessarily%20panicked%20(yet)%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20he%20was%20just%20throwing%20a%20tantrum%20about%20the%20diaper%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20suddenly%2C%20my%20husband%20was%20hurrying%20down%20the%20aisle%20toward%20me%2C%20toddler%20in%20arms.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20sorry%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20low%20voice.%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20mean%20to.%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthree-concussions-turning-point-for-brain-injury-study-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehit%20his%20head%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20heart%20sank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2258765788-ae81-45d2-8565-04ffb8c62ab7%5C%22%3EHe%20had%20been%20hospitalized%20before%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20already%20had%20some%20PTSD%20when%20it%20came%20to%20our%20baby%20son%20Sunny's%20health%20and%20safety.%20At%20just%205%20months%20old%2C%20he%20had%20been%20hospitalized%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcan-adults-get-rsv-infections-common-all-ages-severity-varies-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebad%20case%20of%20RSV%3C%2Fa%3E.%20One%20night%2C%20his%20coughs%20had%20turned%20into%20heaves%20as%20his%20tiny%20chest%20struggled%20to%20breathe%2C%20and%20we%20rushed%20him%20to%20the%20ER.%20From%20there%2C%20they%20took%20him%20in%20an%20ambulance%20to%20a%20pediatric%20hospital%2C%20where%20they%20suctioned%20his%20lungs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20never%20forget%20the%20look%20on%20my%207-year-old's%20face%20as%20he%20watched%20his%20little%20brother%20get%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F4-surprising-medical-costs-how-to-avoid-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etaken%20away%20in%20the%20ambulance%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20begged%20for%20Sunny%20to%20come%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESunny%20did%20come%20back%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20think%20I%20realized%20until%20I%20was%2030%2C000%20feet%20above%20Greenland%20just%20how%20tenuous%20I%20felt%20Sunny's%20continued%20presence%20was.%20Now%2010%20months%20old%2C%20he%20was%20a%20strong%20and%20cheerful%20baby%20%E2%80%94%20but%20he%20was%20still%20a%20baby.%20Fragile%2C%20helpless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cefe9333-fbeb-4148-9f55-0c2f44206a7f%5C%22%3EIt%20was%20an%20accident%20but%20I%20panicked%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20my%20husband%20placed%20him%20in%20my%20lap%20on%20that%20flight%2C%20Sunny%20looked%20up%20at%20me%20with%20wide%2C%20wet%20eyes%2C%20screaming.%20%26quot%3BHead%2C%20mama!%20Head!%26quot%3B%20he%20cried.%20I%20could%20see%20the%20skin%20of%20his%20forehead%20already%20starting%20to%20change%20colors%2C%20forming%20a%20bright%20bump.%20I%20could%20have%20murdered%20my%20husband%20right%20then%20and%20there.%20I%20kept%20thinking%2C%20how%20could%20he%20be%20so%20careless%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20it%20was%20an%20accident%20that%20could%20have%20happened%20to%20anyone%3A%20a%20parent%20scrambling%20to%20change%20a%20squirmy%20toddler's%20dirty%20diaper%20inside%20a%20too-tiny%20airplane%20bathroom.%20The%20parent's%20spatial%20reasoning%20being%20not%20his%20sharpest%20due%20to%2C%20you%20know%2C%20being%20exhausted%20on%20a%20long%20international%20flight%20with%20a%20baby%2C%20he%20steps%20with%20quickness%20and%20confidence%20through%20the%20bathroom%20door%20without%20any%20idea%20that%20in%20doing%20so%2C%20he's%20whacking%20that%20baby's%20soft%20forehead%20sharply%20on%20the%20frame.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20didn't%20help%20that%20I%20was%20working%20as%20a%20parenting%20editor%20at%20the%20time%20and%20was%20immersed%20daily%20in%20an%20excess%20of%20news%20stories%20and%20studies%20about%20all%20things%20baby.%20I%20knew%20very%20well%20how%20serious%20a%20head%20injury%20can%20be%20in%20children.%20I%20had%20read%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Fwalmart-injury-boy-florida-stocking-cart-lawsuit-plaintiff-seizures-2000385%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estory%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FUS%2Fweek-baby-girl-hospitalized-struck-ball-softball-game%2Fstory%3Fid%3D54986660%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estory%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20head%20bumps%20gone%20terribly%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20the%20moment%2C%20as%20my%20sweet%20toddler%20sobbed%20in%20my%20lap%2C%20those%20stories%20were%20all%20that%20filled%20my%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224bb03d35-aa0d-4c34-9ba4-8ca42e2e3d9f%5C%22%3EI%20obsessively%20monitored%20him%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20landed%20in%20Iceland%2C%20our%20destination%2C%20I%20tried%20to%20watch%20for%20any%20of%20the%20telltale%20signs%20of%20distress%20in%20Sunny%3A%20nonstop%20crying%2C%20vomiting%20multiple%20times%2C%20noticeable%20changes%20in%20body%20movements%2C%20sleeping%20more%20than%20normal%2C%20or%20having%20problems%20waking%20up.%20Luckily%2C%20Sunny%20was%20free%20from%20almost%20all%20of%20the%20above%2C%20minus%20sleep%20changes%2C%20which%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-things-for-long-flight-with-little-kid-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeasily%20be%20chalked%20up%20to%20jet%20lag%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20I%20continued%20to%20obsess%20over%20monitoring%20Sunny%20through%20the%20entirety%20of%20our%20trip%20%E2%80%94%20as%20we%20explored%20geysers%20and%20waterfalls%20and%20ate%20cardamom%20buns%20and%20fermented%20shark.%20I%20spent%20sleepless%20nights%20at%20our%20Airbnb%20listening%20to%20Sunny%20breathe%20and%20annoying%20him%20by%20waking%20him%20up%20to%20ensure%20that%20he%20did%2C%20indeed%2C%20wake%20up.%20And%2C%20perhaps%20worst%20of%20all%2C%20I%20continued%20to%20quietly%20blame%20and%20resent%20my%20husband%20for%20the%20injury%3B%20I%20could%20hardly%20look%20at%20him%20the%20whole%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20kids%2C%20however%2C%20forgot%20the%20injury%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%