roperties%2C%20and%20encroachments%20upon%20Waqf%20assets.%20The%20ruling%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20government%20has%20said%20the%20law%20is%20not%20anti-Muslim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20amendment%20was%20introduced%20after%20six%20months%20of%20discussions%2C%20including%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20joint%20parliamentary%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20the%20bill%20was%20passed%20with%20128%20members%20voting%20in%20favour%20and%2095%20opposing%20it.%20It%20was%20passed%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20early%20on%20Thursday%2C%20with%20288%20members%20supporting%20it%20and%20232%20against%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20MP%20Mohammad%20Jawed%2C%20AIMIM%20MP%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%2C%20and%20AAP%20MLA%20Amanatullah%20Khan%20filed%20the%20petitions%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20While%20they%20gave%20many%20reasons%20for%20filing%20the%20petitions%2C%20some%20common%20ones%20include%20allegations%20that%20the%20Waqf%20(Amendment)%20Bill%20-%20now%20an%20Act%20-%20was%20%26quot%3Bdiscriminatory%20towards%20Muslim%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bblatant%20violation%20of%20the%20fundamental%20rights%20of%20Muslims%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20law%20also%20faces%20protests%20from%20the%20All-India%20Muslim%20Personal%20Law%20Board%20(AIMPLB).%20It%20announced%20campaigns%20and%20protests%20across%20the%20country%2C%20focusing%20on%20what%20it%20called%20%26quot%3Bcountering%20misinformation%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bpromoting%20peaceful%20activism%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%2C%20however%2C%20has%20maintained%20that%20the%20law%20will%20benefit%20Muslim%20women%20and%20ensure%20transparency%20in%20managing%20Waqf%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefending%20the%20bill%2C%20BJP%20MP%20Ravi%20Shankar%20Prasad%20told%20NDTV%20it%20would%20bring%20transparency%20by%20making%20Waqf%20boards%20accountable.%20Seeking%20to%20allay%20fears%20that%20the%20law%20would%20take%20away%20Waqf%20properties%2C%20he%20said%20no%20mosque%20or%20graveyard%20is%20going%20to%20be%20touched.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743876540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F5ua1smgg_parliament-session_625x300_10_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaqf-amendment-bill-cleared-by-both-houses-of-parliament-after-heated-debates-gets-presidents-assent-8096268%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20has%20given%20her%20assent%20to%20the%20Waqf%20(Amendment)%20Bill%20which%20was%20passed%20by%20both%20houses%20of%20parliament%20after%20heated%20debates.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaqf-amendment-bill-cleared-by-both-houses-of-parliament-after-heated-debates-gets-presidents-assent-8096268%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Corporate%20affairs%20ministry%20proposes%20changes%20to%20fast-track%20mergers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743875855000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fcorporate-affairs-ministry-proposes-changes-to-fast-track-mergers-125040500949_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ministry%20has%20sought%20public%20comments%20till%20May%205%20on%20the%20proposed%20amendments%20in%20the%20rules%20to%20widen%20the%20scope%20of%20fast-track%20mergers%20under%20the%20Act%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IDF%20admits%20mistakenly%20identifying%20Gaza%20aid%20workers%20as%20threat%20-%20after%20video%20of%20attack%20showed%20ambulances%20were%20marked%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743875280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F25%2F04%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-gaza-aid-workers_6876575.jpg%3F20250405094624%22%2C%