%20process%2C%20she%20told%20me%2C%20and%20we%20found%20that%20to%20be%20true%20in%20our%20home.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225107c5ee-ebdd-413f-bc6b-59e76474fe03%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThey've%20taken%20over%20cooking%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20foundation%20we%20provided%20at%20home%2C%20plus%20skills%20gleaned%20at%20Scout%20camping%20trips%2C%20cooking%20camps%20or%20informal%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchopped-interesting-things-you-never-knew-from-someone-on-show-2022-03%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BChopped%26quot%3B-style%20contests%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20over%20school%20breaks%2C%20gave%20my%20kids%20enough%20interest%20and%20know-how%20to%20want%20to%20help%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20take%20over%20%E2%80%94%20some%20of%20our%20dinner%20prep%20and%20cooking.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGrilled%20cheese%2C%20scrambled%20eggs%2C%20and%20simple%20salads%20were%20among%20their%20early%20dishes%3B%20now%20that%20they%20are%20teens%2C%20they%20often%20assign%20each%20other%20a%20cookbook%20to%20pick%20a%20recipe%20from%20each%20week.%20Sometimes%20it's%20a%20tried-and-true%20Betty%20Crocker%20cookbook%2C%20and%20other%20times%20it's%20a%20tome%20from%20chef%20and%20humanitarian%20Jos%C3%A9%20Andr%C3%A9s.%20Some%20recent%20meals%20they've%20made%20include%20turkey%20bolognese%2C%20spiced%20catfish%20sandwiches%20with%20Haitian%20pickled%20slaw%2C%20and%20gado%20gado%20%E2%80%94%20a%20traditional%20Indonesian%20salad%20that%20I'd%20never%20heard%20of%20until%20our%20son%20prepared%20and%20served%20it%20recently.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gado%20Gado%20dish%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e5821bb8b41a9673fbe260%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20son%20prepared%20a%20dish%20new%20to%20her