iar%20with%20any%20of%20them%2C%20and%20I%20worried%20she'd%20be%20freaked%20out%20seeing%20them%20(some%20for%20the%20first%20time%20ever)%20in%20life-size%20form.%20We'd%20also%20had%20an%20encounter%20with%20an%20Easter%20bunny%20the%20previous%20year%20that%20gave%20me%20pause.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESurprisingly%2C%20she%20was%20only%20a%20little%20apprehensive%20and%20warmed%20up%20to%20them%20very%20quickly.%20By%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Disney%20Jr.%20Play%20and%20Dance%2C%20she%20was%20having%20a%20dance%20party%20with%20Minnie%20Mouse%20and%20giving%20her%20hugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20couldn't%20quite%20work%20up%20the%20nerve%20to%20get%20that%20close%20to%20Goofy%2C%20who%20is%20much%20larger%20than%20Minnie%2C%20but%20all%20these%20months%20later%2C%20she's%20still%20talking%20about%20giving%20Goofy%20a%20high-five%20%26quot%3Bnext%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22meeting%20Goofy%20and%20Max%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ef0083b8b41a9673fc9d54%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221462%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMeeting%20Goofy%20and%20Max%20at%20a%20safe%20distance%20was%20key.%3Cp%3ECaralynn%20Matassa%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20princesses%20were%20an%20even%20bigger%20hit%2C%20and%20it%20was%20such%20a%20joy%20seeing%20her%20interact%20with%20them.%20Princess%20Elena%20was%20her%20favorite%2C%20despite%20never%20having%20watched%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20live%20music%20shows%20were%20also%20a%20great%20choice.%20On%20my%20pre-parenthood%20trips%2C%20I'd%20never%20bothered%20to%20go%20to%20them%20%E2%80%94%20who%20cares%20about%20abbreviated%20versions%20of%20Disney%20movies%20I've%20seen%20a%20trillion%20times%3F%20For%20my%20toddler%2C%20though%2C%20they%20were%20a%20major%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20under%2030%20minutes%2C%20they're%20the%20perfect%20length%20for%20short%20attention%20spans%20and%20a%20great%20primer%20for%20some%20of%20the%20movies%20she%20hadn't%20seen%20yet.%20%26quot%3BFor%20the%20First%20Time%20in%20Forever%3A%20A%20Frozen%20Sing-Along%20Celebration%26quot%3B%20was%20her%20favorite%20and%20has%20sparked%20an%20intense%20Queen%20Elsa%20phase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20safari%20ride%20at%20Animal%20Kingdom%20was%20also%20something%20I'd%20never%20done%2C%20but%20we%20prioritized%20it%20knowing%20my%20toddler's%20love%20of%20zoos.%20It%20was%20a%20major%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2237596054-53a0-42ea-b78b-c3a34f423cf7%5C%22%3EThe%20fireworks%20shows%20were%20always%20a%20highlight%20of%20my%20Disney%20World%20trips%2C%20but%20they%20were%20too%20much%20for%20my%20toddler%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3BFantasmic!%26quot%3B%20show%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-hollywood-studios-attractions-ranking-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHollywood%20Studios%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20my%20single%20favorite%20Disney%20experience%2C%20and%20I've%20always%20made%20a%20point%20to%20go%20multiple%20times%20during%20each%20of%20my%20past%20trips.%20However%2C%20we%20didn't%20even%20consider%20going%20with%20my%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20never%20experienced%20a%20fireworks%20show%20before%2C%20so%20to%20test%20the%20waters%2C%20we%20took%20her%20to%20%26quot%3BLuminous%3A%20The%20Symphony%20of%20Us%2C%26quot%3B%20a%2017-minute%20show%20in%20Epcot.%20We%20watched%20from%20the%20World%20Showcase%20because%20I%20figured%20that%20was%20far%20enough%20away%20from%20the%20sights%20and%20sounds%20not%20to%20be%20too%20overwhelming.%20I%20was%20extremely%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22fireworks%20at%20Epcot%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eef787b8b41a9673fc9bee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Epcot%20fireworks%20show%20was%20a%20big%20no.%3Cp%3ECaralynn%20Matassa%2F