ng-which-is-better-review-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWalmart%20grocery%20bill%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20month%20was%20%241%2C923%2C%20I%20felt%20the%20guilt%20creep%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20then%2C%20he%20said%20something%20that%20I%20didn't%20expect%3A%20%26quot%3BLet%20me%20take%20over%20the%20grocery%20shopping.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20laughed.%20Not%20because%20I%20thought%20he'd%20do%20a%20bad%20job%20but%20because%20I%20couldn't%20imagine%20it%20would%20make%20any%20real%20difference.%20Plus%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-save-money-groceries-budget-hacks-discounts-frugal-food-plan-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrocery%20shopping%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20my%20domain%3A%20I%20knew%20what%20we%20liked%2C%20and%20I%20meal%20planned.%20I%20didn't%20love%20the%20idea%20of%20him%20double-checking%20my%20choices.%20But%20I%20was%20exhausted%20from%20the%20weekly%20trips%2C%20so%20I%20handed%20him%20the%20grocery%20list%20%E2%80%94%20half%20expecting%20him%20to%20come%20back%20overwhelmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20month%2C%20our%20grocery%20bill%20dropped%20to%20%241%2C511.%20I%20figured%20he%20was%20just%20cutting%20corners%20to%20prove%20he%20could%20spend%20less.%20But%20the%20following%20month%3F%20%241%2C555.%20Our%20pantry%20was%20full%2C%20our%20kids%20were%20happy%2C%20and%20we%20were%20spending%20around%20%24400%20less%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20to%20admit%3A%20maybe%20my%20husband%20was%20onto%20something.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2210db9c48-55be-40f8-82dc-40bc61297fee%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHe%20started%20by%20taking%20his%20time%20in%20the%20store%20to%20consider%20all%20the%20options%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20curious%20about%20his%20method%3A%20%26quot%3BHow%20are%20you%20doing%20this%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20turns%20out%20his%20first%20grocery%20shopping%20trip%20took%20almost%20two%20hours%20%E2%80%94%20and%20not%20because%20he%20couldn't%20find%20anything.%20While%20I%20was%20home%20imagining%20him%20wandering%20lost%20in%20the%20aisles%2C%20he%20was%20carefully%20reading%20ads%20(the%20ones%20I%20would%20have%20tossed%20aside)%20and%20checking%20prices%20on%20every%20single%20item.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEver%20the%20engineer%2C%20my%20husband%20pulled%20out%20his%20phone%20to%20show%20me%20some%20of%20the%20side-by-side%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-vs-target-grocery-shopping-which-is-better-review-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprice%20comparisons%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20made.%20I%20was%20beyond%20surprised.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2295f8b43f-9972-45ea-b65e-48adb3eaf3a3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20husband%20made%20some%20big%20money-saving%20switches%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20kids%20go%20through%20ketchup%20like%20water.%20I%20had%20been%20buying%20Heinz%20at%20%244.48%20for%20years%20without%20thinking%20twice.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-walmart-brand-cream-cheese-highlights-the-problem-with-the-us-economy-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGreat%20Value%20brand%3C%2Fa%3E%20my%20husband%20chose%20is%20just%20%241.92%20for%20the%20same%20size%20bottle%2C%20and%20it%20tastes%20exactly%20the%20same%2C%20saving%20us%20%242.56%20every%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Heinz%20ketchup%20next%20to%20cheaper%20generic%20ketchup%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eaf9a8b8b41a9673fc3637%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20generic%20brand%20of%20ketchup%20is%20cheaper.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Amy%20Braun%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20ranch%20savings%20may%20be%20one%20of%20our%20biggest.%20Switching%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhich-brand-has-best-ranch-dressing-grocery-store-ranking%5