0and%20absorbent%20inserts%20that%20can%20be%20fixed%20with%20straps%20%E2%80%94%20a%20flexible%2C%20low-waste%20alternative%20to%20disposable%20pads%2C%20priced%20at%20Rs%20180%20for%20a%203-month%20supply.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pad%20is%20not%20leak-proof%20%E2%80%94%20intentionally%20so.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20took%20a%20conscious%20decision%20not%20to%20coat%20it%20with%20polymers%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20environment%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProject%20Uger%20garnered%20national%20and%20international%20recognition%20and%20is%20now%20being%20replicated%20across%20the%20country.%20In%20an%20unusual%20but%20powerful%20move%2C%20Lakshmi%20chose%20not%20to%20copyright%20the%20Uger%20design.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20Self-Help%20Groups%20(SHGs)%20have%20copied%20the%20pad.%20We%20helped%20four%20SHGs%20in%20Northeast%20India%20set%20up%20units%20to%20make%20it.%20The%20Aditya%20Birla%20Group%20runs%20a%20unit%20in%20Jalna%2C%20Maharashtra.%20Mitu%20Foundation%20in%20Bengaluru%20is%20making%20it%20too.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pad%20was%20intentionally%20kept%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9CCopy%20Left%E2%80%9D%20space%2C%20a%20decision%20that%20allowed%20anyone%20to%20replicate%20the%20design%20without%20legal%20restriction.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20a%20conscious%20choice%20to%20ensure%20the%20product%20reached%20as%20many%20people%20as%20possible%2C%20without%20commercial%20barriers%2C%E2%80%9D%20Lakshmi%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%202876px)%20100vw%2C%202876px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FFolded-pads_11zon-1743519258.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222876%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Reusable%20cotton%20pads%20from%20Project%20Uger%20%E2%80%94%20eco-friendly%2C%20affordable%2C%20and%20designed%20to%20be%20stitched%20and%20sold%20by%20rural%20women.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22ht